    "SET_URB_AGG": {
      "name": "Urban Agglomeration",
      "definition": "An extended city or town area comprising the built-up area of a central place and any suburbs linked by continuous urban development. It represents a setting characterized by high population density and vast human-made features in comparison to surrounding rural areas. This term functions as an integrated economic and social unit regardless of administrative boundaries, reflecting the physical spread of urbanization.",
