    "SET_CMD": {
      "name": "Commercial District",
      "definition": "An area primarily zoned for business, retail, and trade activities. This setting is characterized by a high concentration of shops, offices, and service providers. Morphologically, it features high pedestrian and vehicular traffic, commercial signage, and land use strictly dedicated to economic exchange rather than residential or industrial purposes, often serving as a node of high activity intensity.",
